== QFS_(disambiguation) ==
QFS may mean, * [[QFS|SAM-QFS (Storage and Archive Manager - Quick File System)]], an open source filesystem from Sun Microsystems. * [[Quantcast_File_System_(QFS)|QFS (Quantcast File System)]], an open-source distributed file system software package for large-scale MapReduce/batch-processing workloads.
{{disambig}}
